    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors reviewed. Seven factors assessed; all achieved levels fall below required levels for MRL 5. Six factors flagged as not-assessed epistemic gaps. Monte Carlo UQ demonstrates large parametric uncertainty (±45% at 95th percentile). Mesh-independence claim is recorded in the assessment register and benchmark evidence is cited in the narrative; however the structured derivation link from claim to evidence was not formalised prior to submission. Overall credibility is insufficient for a Class III VAD absolute hemolysis threshold decision. Assessment outcome is not accepted pending resolution of all identified gaps.",
